OL,3,CUS state visit risk 'grasped in both
OL,4,Chands' by King, aide says
OL,6,FMuch has been made of the personal
OL,7,Frelationship between the King and US
OL,8,FPresident Donald Trump, and the senior
OL,9,Fpalace aide involved in the trip said
OL,10,Fthe two men "get on very well", and
OL,11,F"the warmth that you see in public is
OL,12,Fabsolutely the warmth you see in
OL,13,Fprivate".
OL,15,FWhen asked if it was awkward for the
OL,16,Fpresident to have a warmer
OL,17,Frelationship with the King than the
OL,18,FPrime Minister, the aide replied:
OL,19,F"It's not a competition between the
OL,20,FKing and the Government.
OL,26,@rD@MOUrD@^O]sD@AOUuD@HO]{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
