OL,3,CUS state visit risk 'grasped in both
OL,4,Chands' by King, aide says
OL,6,F"The King is there to support the
OL,7,FGovernment, to help the Government. It
OL,8,Fwas at the Government's request, of
OL,9,Fcourse, that he undertook this visit."
OL,11,FThe Congress address made by the King
OL,12,Fhas been widely interpreted as a
OL,13,Fgentle push back against some of Mr
OL,14,FTrump's pet peeves ` Ukraine, Nato,
OL,15,Fthe need to follow rules and the
OL,16,Fclimate change lobby.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
