OL,3,CUS state visit risk 'grasped in both
OL,4,Chands' by King, aide says
OL,6,FBut he was guided by the "truth" and
OL,7,Fhis "conscience" when delivering his
OL,8,Fspeech that found favour with many
OL,9,FRepublicans and Democrats, and its
OL,10,Fcontents were "a measure of how much
OL,11,Fhe personally cares".
OL,13,FAhead of the visit, Downing Street's
OL,14,Frequest was seen as a throw of the
OL,15,Fdice, with the King being sent to help
OL,16,Frepair the UK-US special relationship
OL,17,Ffollowing repeated criticisms levelled
OL,18,Fby Mr Trump at Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,19,FStarmer over the war in Iran.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUnD@`O]oD@EOUoD@PO]rD@OOUsD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
