OL,3,CUS state visit risk 'grasped in both
OL,4,Chands' by King, aide says
OL,6,FThe monarchy's soft power diplomacy is
OL,7,Fseen as its strongest weapon in
OL,8,Fsupport of the UK's overseas interests
OL,9,Fand it appears Mr Trump was won over
OL,10,Fduring the four days, repeatedly
OL,11,Fpraising "fantastic" Charles.
OL,13,FA parting gift came from his host Mr
OL,14,FTrump, who lifted tariffs on Scottish
OL,15,Fwhisky after an intervention by the
OL,16,FQueen and King.
OL,26,@sD@JOUsD@TO]
