OL,3,CUS state visit risk 'grasped in both
OL,4,Chands' by King, aide says
OL,6,FThe senior palace aide said about the
OL,7,Frelationship between the two world
OL,8,Ffigures and their wives: "They get on
OL,9,Fvery well. And it's not just the King
OL,10,Fand the president. It's all four of
OL,11,Fthem with each other."
OL,13,FHe added: "It's a pairing, sort of
OL,14,Funlikely though it might be in many
OL,15,Fways ... I mean, given some of the
OL,16,Fissues that have presented themselves
OL,17,Fin the bilateral relationship, you'd
OL,18,Fthink it might all be a bit tricky.
OL,19,FBut far from it.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUsD@VO]uD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
