OL,3,CUS state visit risk 'grasped in both
OL,4,Chands' by King, aide says
OL,6,F"And the warmth that you see in public
OL,7,Fis absolutely the warmth you see in
OL,8,Fprivate."
OL,10,FWhen the King and the President sat
OL,11,Fdown in the Oval Office for their
OL,12,Fbilateral meeting, there was lots of
OL,13,F"laughter" alongside the serious talk.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@IO]uD@AOUuD@JO]
