OL,3,CUS state visit risk 'grasped in both
OL,4,Chands' by King, aide says
OL,6,FRepublicans and Democrats rose to
OL,7,Ftheir feet 12 times to applaud during
OL,8,FCharles' speech in Congress' Hall of
OL,9,Fthe House, where the King spoke of the
OL,10,Fimportance of Nato, support for
OL,11,FUkraine, the value of European
OL,12,Fpartners and the need to reduce world
OL,13,Fconflicts, all priorities for Sir
OL,14,FKeir's Government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
