PN,30212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777770201
OL,3,CUS state visit risk 'grasped in both
OL,4,Chands' by King, aide says
OL,6,F"And three, they're all observable
OL,7,Ffacts. Everything that is in that
OL,8,Fspeech is an observable fact. And so,
OL,9,FI think we felt very comfortable with
OL,10,Fthe King speaking as he did."
OL,12,FThe positive response to the US speech
OL,13,Fand the rapport between the president
OL,14,Fand the King have all helped to put
OL,15,Fthe special relationship on a firmer
OL,16,Ffooting, especially during the 250th
OL,17,Fanniversary year of American
OL,18,Findependence.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@]O]
