OL,3,CUS state visit risk 'grasped in both
OL,4,Chands' by King, aide says
OL,6,FCharles' four-day visit was followed
OL,7,Fby a solo trip to Bermuda to celebrate
OL,8,Fits culture, people and achievements
OL,9,Fwhich ended on Saturday.
OL,11,FThe aide added: "The King has greatly
OL,12,Fenjoyed it.
OL,14,F"It has been very busy and the crowds
OL,15,Fhave been so huge they have made us
OL,16,Fextremely late, but no-one minds about
OL,17,Fthat when you feel that you're doing
OL,18,Fsome good here, showing that this
OL,19,Fisland matters to Britain, because it
OL,20,Fcertainly matters to the King."
OL,26,@sD@QOUvD@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
