OL,3,CUS state visit risk 'grasped in both
OL,4,Chands' by King, aide says
OL,6,FCharles is still receiving treatment
OL,7,Ffor an undisclosed form of cancer but
OL,8,Fremains dedicated to his role.
OL,10,F"This is a man who is absolutely
OL,11,Fdriven by duty. Driven by service,"
OL,12,Fsaid the aide.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@cO]
